# Clockwork Codeflow & Internal Mechanism

This document breaks down the specific mechanistic codeflow and life cycle of the **Clockwork System**, mapping exactly what happens natively across the internal Python class abstractions to accomplish its goals. It includes a comprehensive flowchart of the internal connections, followed by a file-by-file breakdown detailing the purpose and link of each component.

